comments: Harrell (LAL) extends his right hand forward and marginal contact occurs with Olynyk's (HOU) left elbow along the perimeter.
Harrell (LAL) has his left hand on Olynyk's (HOU) left hip and quickly slides it off.
Kuzma (LAL) draws Tate (HOU) into the air toward him and the contact results in a foul on Tate even if contact is initiated by Kuzma.
Olynyk (HOU) makes contact with the ball and the part of Kuzma's (LAL) hand that is on the ball, and dislodges it away before any incidental contact occurs.
Harrell (LAL) establishes himself in a screening position in Tate's (HOU) path and absorbs the contact.
Olynyk (HOU) maintains a legal guarding position as he cleanly deflects the ball away from Horton-Tucker (LAL).

Horton-Tucker (LAL) and Tate (HOU) come together at the same spot following the turnover and incidental contact occurs as they turn to move in transition. Tate's reaction is not consistent with the amount of contact.
Harrell (LAL) engages and disengages with Olynyk (HOU) as he moves to set the pick.
Olynyk (HOU) is deemed to be in the lane for less than three seconds when the shot is imminent.
Kuzma (LAL) brings his arm down and initiates contact with Martin Jr.'s (HOU) right arm during his upward shooting motion.
Harrell (LAL) engages and disengages with Olynyk (HOU) during rebounding.
Martin Jr. (HOU) grasps and then quickly releases Kuzma's (LAL) jersey off ball.
Caldwell-Pope (LAL) uses his left hand to initiate contact with Thomas' (HOU) side, dislodging Thomas from position as they move along the perimeter.
Olynyk (HOU) brings his right hand toward Harrell's (LAL) right arm and marginal contact occurs as Olynyk starts his drive.
Olynyk (HOU) gathers the ball and takes two steps before attempting the shot.
Harrell (LAL) initiates contact across Olynyk's (HOU) right arm that affects the driving shot attempt.
Horton-Tucker (LAL) brings his off-arm toward Tate's (HOU) front and marginal contact occurs as Horton-Tucker naturally releases away.
Tate (HOU) moves toward Horton-Tucker (LAL) and marginal body contact occurs after Horton-Tucker picks his dribble up in the lane.
Horton-Tucker (LAL) moves his pivot foot after picking up his dribble in the lane.
Harrell (LAL) is deemed to be imminently exiting the lane within three seconds.
Martin Jr. (HOU) moves alongside Kuzma's (LAL) path and absorbs the marginal body contact that occurs as Kuzma changes direction after his gather.

Tate (HOU) establishes himself in a screening position in Horton-Tucker's (LAL) path and absorbs the contact. Tate's momentum subsequently takes him out of bounds and any contact that occurs with Horton-Tucker thereafter occurs after the expiration of the screen.
Matthews (LAL) swipes forward and cleanly dislodges the ball away from Olynyk (HOU).
Tate (HOU) commits a take foul on Horton-Tucker (LAL).
